Register a bucket as an NFSv4 export

Usage:
  grainfs nfs export add <bucket> [flags]

Flags:
      --dry-run   validate only; do not propose change
  -h, --help      help for add
      --json      emit machine-readable JSON output
      --quiet     suppress stdout on success
      --ro        register as read-only export

Global Flags:
      --endpoint string    admin Unix socket path (required, e.g. ./tmp/admin.sock)
      --log-level string   log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")
      --timeout duration   admin command timeout (e.g. 30s, 5m); unset = 30s default; 0 = uncapped (for long follow loops)
